<p style="text-align: center;"> <a style="text-align: center;" data-udi="umb://document/b741a67aaee94a26bd6d0e0112846efc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b741a67aaee94a26bd6d0e0112846efc}" title="Hotel &amp; Spa Le Savoie" class="c-btn">Hotel Le Savoie</a><span style="text-align: center;"> </span><a style="text-align: center;" data-udi="umb://document/6bfba831952648e4914c5b747bee97f3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6bfba831952648e4914c5b747bee97f3}" title="Hotel De Champoluc" class="c-btn">Hotel De Champoluc</a><span style="text-align: center;"> </span><a style="text-align: center;" data-udi="umb://document/91c84340449f44b88b68bda04ef761d8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/91c84340449f44b88b68bda04ef761d8}" title="Hotel des Deux Domaines" class="c-btn">Hotel des Deux Domaines</a><span style="text-align: center;"> </span><a style="text-align: center;" data-udi="umb://document/a974436a181a43c193afabccefad916d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a974436a181a43c193afabccefad916d}" title="Hotel Ducs De Savoie" class="c-btn">Hotel Ducs de Savoie</a> <a style="text-align: center;" data-udi="umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257}" title="Chalets" class="c-btn">Chalets</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13109436/1550-child-places-table-updated.jpg" alt="SpecialOfferChildPlaces" data-udi="umb://media/2acf04b4647147158f7348ec2fe93bb6" /></p>
<p> </p>
