<p style="text-align: center;"><span><a style="text-align: center;" data-udi="umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257}" title="Chalets" class="c-btn">View chalets</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<h3>Terms and Conditions</h3>
<ul>
<li>Hotel De Champoluc is a Sunday departure, Hotel des Deux Domaines, Hotel Ducs de Savoie and Hotel Le Savoie and all chalets are Saturday departures.</li>
<li>Chalets can be booked by families either during peak-dates including Christmas, New Year, Half-Term and Easter or for exclusive use on all dates. Otherwise, chalets include children of 12 years of age and above only.</li>
<li>The reductions are off the basic adult holiday price, not including room/airport supplements, insurance, childcare, ski-packs etc, which are payable in full.</li>
<li>Discount is dependant on flight route taken.</li>
<li>Our reservations team can assist with any questions or your booking: 01483791111, otherwise the discount will automatically be applied when booking online.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
